<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Verify your email address</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #2563eb;">Welcome to TESDA Calendar</h2>
        
        <p>Thank you for registering with TESDA Calendar. To complete your registration, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="{{ verification_url }}" 
               style="background-color: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block;">
                Verify Email Address
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <p>If the button doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
        <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #2563eb;">{{ verification_url }}</p>
        
        <p><strong>Note:</strong> This verification link will expire in 24 hours.</p>
        
        <hr style="margin: 30px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee;">
        
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
            If you didn't create an account with TESDA Calendar, you can safely ignore this email.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>